high_descs: Look on the stove and counter and browse up and down.
Pick up the knife on the right side by the potato.
Turn around, go to the end of the kitchen, turn right to face the microwave.
Slice the first tomato above the spoon in half.
Turn right, step forward, then turn left to be center with the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the knife inside, close the door.
Return to the sliced tomato next to the microwave.
Pick up the first slice of tomato from the left.
Step forward to be centered with the microwave.
Open microwave, place tomato inside and turn on.  Wait a few seconds till off, open door to pick up tomato slice, close microwave.
Turn left, step forward, turn right to the counter.
Place the tomato slice to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Cook a slice of tomato in microwave and place next to the spoon.

high_descs: Look under the stove at the oven.
Take the knife from the counter to the right of the stove.
Turn around and walk past the sink, the turn right and walk to the table with the microwave on it next to the refrigerator.
Slice the tomato on the table next to the microwave.
Turn and open the microwave door on your right.
Place the knife in the microwave next to the green cup and close the door.
Turn back to the sliced tomato on the table.
Pick up one slice of tomato.
Turn and take the tomato slice to the microwave on your right.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave and cook for seven seconds, then take the tomato slice out
Take the cooked tomato slice and turn to the other tomato slices on the table.
Place the cooked tomato slice on the table next to the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Cut the tomato with the knife and cook one slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around, walk across the room, then turn right and cross the room to face the tomato.
Cut the front tomato on the microwave into slices.
Step to the right and face the microwave.
Place the knife into the microwave.
Step to the left and face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the tomato on the counter.
Step to the right and turn to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Step to the left and face the counter.
Place the tomato slice on the counter beside the spoon.
anns.task_desc: To cut plus heat a slice of tomato as well as place it on the counter.
